  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♦9 maps! 9 shiny herbs! 9 ways!<br>kill the enemy, Collect clues and trace it<br>-BK-</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♦Story</h2>With big eyes, short legs, and big fists, <br>The young man's name is 'InJeong'<br><br>In this journey,<br>Those who disturb me, i will crash them in my fist!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/ce0e7b7c6f218facd567320950908aef.poster.avif?t=1667014064\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/ce0e7b7c6f218facd567320950908aef.webm?t=1667014064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/ce0e7b7c6f218facd567320950908aef.mp4?t=1667014064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Where is it?<br>Shining herbs are hidden,<br>kill the enemies, Collect information and look for clues<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/069cc974b0a31e391c59aba8d4be2af0.poster.avif?t=1667014064\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/069cc974b0a31e391c59aba8d4be2af0.webm?t=1667014064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/069cc974b0a31e391c59aba8d4be2af0.mp4?t=1667014064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♦About Game</h2>▪ This is a story about the young man's journey,<br>Explore the map and find a shiny herb<br>9 maps! 9 shiny herbs! 9 ways!<br>open world! Your movement is free!<br><br>▪ I am tough guy! Let's do the punching, throwing the stone and defeating the enemy<br>(you can use Hot punch!)<br>Dialogue with npc and monsters, collect clues<br>Sometimes you may need gifts item for them<br><br>▪ Collect the money and items<br>Collect the bead of life<br>Level up ability and get stronger!<br><br>▪ During the journey, find a 'book for travelers' and learn the skills,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/ee8aa3a0afbf7f0069e09e09dae8405c.webp?t=1667014064\" width=527 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♦And...</h2>▪ Can you collect all shiny herbs?<br>it's not an easy journey. but... Don't give up!",
