br>Dialogue with npc and monsters, collect clues<br>Sometimes you may need gifts item for them<br><br>▪ Collect the money and items<br>Collect the bead of life<br>Level up ability and get stronger!<br><br>▪ During the journey, find a 'book for travelers' and learn the skills,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/813920/extras/ee8aa3a0afbf7f0069e09e09dae8405c.webp?t=1667014064\" width=527 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♦And...</h2>▪ Can you collect all shiny herbs?<br>it's not an easy journey. but... Don't give up!",
